name: Piano Lesson
description:
Part of a new series of black and white images based on the idea of small, everyday pleasures and curiosities...

This photograph is a contact print measuring 4" x 5" inches on 8"x 10" paper. There is a black border around the image.

Printed by hand in a traditional black and white darkroom on Ilford paper. Edition of 25.

Signed, numbered, and shipped flat and well protected.

*Available as a larger print by request.
